name: LONELINESS
description:
It is cruel when we don't have the company of another person to survive, it drives us to do things we don't want to do, to get close to treacherous and unfriendly creatures just to fill the emptiness someone else left in our heart and satisfy a need of our own ¡How selfish! Maybe a little food, maybe a little water, maybe a little love and care will help tame the crow and cure my loneliness
